### Welcome to beyonce.horse!
Yes, this is a real website! It is owned and operated by writer and humorist [Graham Starr](gstarr.github.io). There is nothing here currently but there probably will be at some point in the future. In the meantime, feel free to check out my other (more official) [website](http://gstarr.github.io/), or follow me on [Twitter](http://twitter.com/grahamstarr).
